plot:
In "Parlamentet" we see the best Swedish comedians in disguise try dirty
 tricks on politicians and give their own obstinate solutions to 
Sweden's problems. After several seasons with Hans Rosenfeld as host, 
this spring Henrik Schyffert took over. In the blue team we meet Sissela
 Kyle, Helge Skoog, Johan Wahlström and Mikael Tornving. In the red team
 we meet Johan Ulveson, Henrik Hjelt, Annika Lantz and Babben Larsson. 
"Parlamentet" is based on the original idea "If I ruled the world" from 
Hat Trick. Fuente: IMDb
